    "author_association": "MEMBER",
    "body": "The issue is that -\r\n1) A timer is being set with a callback to &t->retry_initiate_ping_locked in maybe_initiate_ping. [source](https://github.com/grpc/grpc/blob/100e0a78ebc1ecfaefb57c5105506b3091d4b86c/src/core/ext/transport/chttp2/transport/writing.cc#L91)\r\n2) A ref on transport is not being taken when we initialize the timer.\r\n3) This means that if the timer fires after the transport is destroyed then it will result in a heap use-after-free resulting in possible SEGFAULTs"
  },
